forma.lms is an Open Source e-Learning platform (LMS and LCMS) used in corporate and higher education markets.

The Platform supports 25 languages, it's compliant with the SCORM 1.2 and 2004 standards, and supports different didactic models, including: Blended, Self-Directed, Collaborative and even Social Learning through Chat, Wiki, Forums and other different functions.
